exceptional4j 

Current Version
===============
0.0.1-SNAPSHOT

Brief
=====
This Java library is a small client API to the getexceptional.com exception-handling service. You can embed this library in your code and broadcast any exceptions that occur within your code back to getexceptional.com.

Build Requirements 
==================
Java 5.0
Maven 2


Usage Requirements
==================
Java 5.0
Jakarta Commons HttpClient 3.1 - http://hc.apache.org/httpclient-3.x/
google-gson 1.3b2 - http://code.google.com/p/google-gson/

